966static uint16_T look1_iu16lu64n48_binlcse(uint16_T u0, const uint16_T bp0[],



967  const uint16_T table[], uint32_T maxIndex)



968{



969  uint16_T y;



970  uint64_T frac;



971  uint32_T iRght;



972  uint32_T iLeft;



973  uint32_T bpIdx;



974



975  /* Lookup 1-D



976     Search method: 'binary'



977     Use previous index: 'off'



978     Interpolation method: 'Linear point-slope'



979     Extrapolation method: 'Clip'



980     Use last breakpoint for index at or above upper limit: 'off'



981     Remove protection against out-of-range input in generated code: 'off'



982     Rounding mode: 'simplest'



983   */



984  /* Prelookup - Index and Fraction



985     Index Search method: 'binary'



986     Extrapolation method: 'Clip'



987     Use previous index: 'off'



988     Use last breakpoint for index at or above upper limit: 'off'



989     Remove protection against out-of-range input in generated code: 'off'



990     Rounding mode: 'simplest'



991   */



992  if (u0 <= bp0[0U]) {



993    iLeft = 0U;



994    frac = 0ULL;



995  } else if (u0 < bp0[maxIndex]) {



996    /* Binary Search */



997    bpIdx = maxIndex >> 1U;



998    iLeft = 0U;



999    iRght = maxIndex;



1000    while (iRght - iLeft > 1U) {



1001      if (u0 < bp0[bpIdx]) {



1002        iRght = bpIdx;



1003      } else {



1004        iLeft = bpIdx;



1005      }



1006



1007      bpIdx = (iRght + iLeft) >> 1U;



1008    }



1009



1010    frac = ((uint64_T)(uint16_T)((uint32_T)u0 - bp0[iLeft]) << 48) / (uint16_T)



1011      ((uint32_T)bp0[iLeft + 1U] - bp0[iLeft]);



1012  } else {



1013    iLeft = maxIndex - 1U;



1014    frac = 281474976710656ULL;



1015  }



1016



1017  /* Interpolation 1-D



1018     Interpolation method: 'Linear point-slope'



1019     Use last breakpoint for index at or above upper limit: 'off'



1020     Rounding mode: 'simplest'



1021     Overflow mode: 'wrapping'



1022   */



1023  if (table[iLeft + 1U] >= table[iLeft]) {



1024    y = (uint16_T)((uint32_T)(uint16_T)(((uint16_T)((uint32_T)table[iLeft + 1U]



1025      - table[iLeft]) * frac) >> 48) + table[iLeft]);



1026  } else {



1027    y = (uint16_T)((uint32_T)table[iLeft] - (uint16_T)(((uint16_T)((uint32_T)



1028      table[iLeft] - table[iLeft + 1U]) * frac) >> 48));



1029  }



1030



1031  return y;



1032}

2267  localDW->Integrator_DSTATE = Integrator;

2329static int32_T Gearshift_getTime(void)



2330{



2331  int32_T time;



2332  if (rtDW.is_UPSHIFTING == IN_UP_START) {



2333    if (rtDW.is_NEUTRAL_STATE == IN_SET_NEUTRAL) {



2334      time = rtDW.UnitDelay1[(int32_T)DEFAULT_NT_CLUTCH_DELAY];



2335    } else {



2336      time = rtDW.UnitDelay1[(int32_T)DELAY];



2337    }



2338  } else if (rtDW.is_UPSHIFTING == IN_UP_PUSH) {



2339    if (rtDW.is_NEUTRAL_STATE == IN_SET_NEUTRAL) {



2340      time = rtDW.UnitDelay1[(int32_T)NT_CLUTCH_DELAY];



2341    } else {



2342      switch (rtDW.RateTransition36[6]) {



2343       case 1:



2344        time = rtDW.UnitDelay1[(int32_T)UP_PUSH_1_2];



2345        break;



2346



2347       case 2:



2348        time = rtDW.UnitDelay1[(int32_T)UP_PUSH_2_3];



2349        break;



2350



2351       case 3:



2352        time = rtDW.UnitDelay1[(int32_T)UP_PUSH_3_4];



2353        break;



2354



2355       case 4:



2356        time = rtDW.UnitDelay1[(int32_T)UP_PUSH_4_5];



2357        break;



2358



2359       default:



2360        time = rtDW.UnitDelay1[(int32_T)UP_PUSH_2_3];



2361        break;



2362      }



2363    }



2364  } else if (rtDW.is_UPSHIFTING == IN_UP_REBOUND) {



2365    if (rtDW.is_NEUTRAL_STATE == IN_SET_NEUTRAL) {



2366      time = rtDW.UnitDelay1[(int32_T)NT_REBOUND_1_N];



2367    } else {



2368      time = rtDW.UnitDelay1[(int32_T)UP_REBOUND];



2369    }



2370  } else if (rtDW.is_UPSHIFTING == IN_UP_BRAKE) {



2371    if (rtDW.is_NEUTRAL_STATE == IN_SET_NEUTRAL) {



2372      time = rtDW.UnitDelay1[(int32_T)NT_BRAKE_1_N];



2373    } else {



2374      time = rtDW.UnitDelay1[(int32_T)UP_BRAKE];



2375    }



2376  } else if (rtDW.is_DOWNSHIFTING == IN_DOWN_START) {



2377    time = rtDW.UnitDelay1[(int32_T)CLUTCH];



2378  } else if (rtDW.is_DOWNSHIFTING == IN_DOWN_PUSH) {



2379    time = rtDW.UnitDelay1[(int32_T)DN_PUSH];



2380  } else if (rtDW.is_DOWNSHIFTING == IN_DOWN_REBOUND) {



2381    time = rtDW.UnitDelay1[(int32_T)DN_REBOUND];



2382  } else {



2383    time = rtDW.UnitDelay1[(int32_T)DN_BRAKE];



2384  }

2386  return time;



2387}

2726static void checkShift(void)



2727{



2728  int32_T b_previousEvent;



2729  if (rtDW.RateTransition2[0] != rtDW.lastShiftCom) {



2730    rtDW.lastShiftCom = rtDW.RateTransition2[0];

2732      b_previousEvent = rtDW.sfEvent;



2733      rtDW.sfEvent = event_GearshiftUp;



2734      if (rtDW.is_active_NEUTRAL_STATE != 0U) {



2735        NEUTRAL_STATE();



2736      }



2737



2738      rtDW.sfEvent = event_GearshiftUp;



2739      if (rtDW.is_active_GEARSHIFT != 0U) {



2740        GEARSHIFT();



2741      }



2742



2743      rtDW.sfEvent = b_previousEvent;



2744    } else if (rtDW.RateTransition2[1] == GEAR_COMMAND_DOWN) {



2745      b_previousEvent = rtDW.sfEvent;



2746      rtDW.sfEvent = event_GearshiftDown;



2747      if (rtDW.is_active_NEUTRAL_STATE != 0U) {



2748        NEUTRAL_STATE();



2749      }



2750



2751      rtDW.sfEvent = event_GearshiftDown;



2752      if (rtDW.is_active_GEARSHIFT != 0U) {



2753        GEARSHIFT();



2754      }



2755



2756      rtDW.sfEvent = b_previousEvent;



2757    } else if (rtDW.RateTransition2[1] == GEAR_COMMAND_NEUTRAL_UP) {



2758      b_previousEvent = rtDW.sfEvent;



2759      rtDW.sfEvent = event_GearshiftSetNeutral;



2760      if (rtDW.is_active_NEUTRAL_STATE != 0U) {



2761        NEUTRAL_STATE();



2762      }



2763



2764      rtDW.sfEvent = event_GearshiftUp;



2765      if (rtDW.is_active_GEARSHIFT != 0U) {



2766        GEARSHIFT();



2767      }



2768



2769      rtDW.sfEvent = b_previousEvent;



2770    } else {



2771      if (rtDW.RateTransition2[1] == GEAR_COMMAND_NEUTRAL_DOWN) {



2772        b_previousEvent = rtDW.sfEvent;



2773        rtDW.sfEvent = event_GearshiftSetNeutral;



2774        if (rtDW.is_active_NEUTRAL_STATE != 0U) {



2775          NEUTRAL_STATE();



2776        }



2777



2778        rtDW.sfEvent = event_GearshiftDown;



2779        if (rtDW.is_active_GEARSHIFT != 0U) {



2780          GEARSHIFT();



2781        }
